      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Liverpool boiler installation prices from £1,800 to £4,500+. Here is a clear breakdown by boiler type, what affects your quote and what Liverpool homeowners actually pay in 2026.</p>
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <span><strong>By</strong> Ideal Plumbing Solutions</span>
        <span><strong>Gas Safe Registered Engineers</strong></span>
        <span>April 2026</span>
